<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/" xmlns:sch="http://api.jasperwireless.com/ws/schema">
   <soapenv:Header> 
      <wsse:Security soapenv:mustUnderstand="1" xmlns:wsse="http://docs.oasis-open.org/wss/2004/01/oasis-200401-wss-wssecurity-secext-1.0.xsd"> 
            <wsse:UsernameToken> 
            <wsse:Username>{{USERNAME}}</wsse:Username> 
            <wsse:Password Type="http://docs.oasis-open.org/wss/2004/01/oasis-200401-wss-username-token-profile-1.0#PasswordText">{{PASSWORD}}</wsse:Password> 
         </wsse:UsernameToken> 
      </wsse:Security> 
   </soapenv:Header>
   <soapenv:Body>
      <sch:AdvanceShipmentNotificationRequest>
         <sch:messageId>{{MESSAGEID}}</sch:messageId>
         <sch:version>{{VERSION}}</sch:version>
         <sch:licenseKey>{{LICENSEKEY}}</sch:licenseKey>
         <sch:orderId>{{ORDERID}}</sch:orderId>
         <!--Optional:-->
         <sch:statusUpdateNote>{{STATUSUPDATENOTE}}</sch:statusUpdateNote>
         <sch:orderLineItems>
            <sch:orderLineItem>
               <sch:shipments>
                  <sch:shipment>
                     <!--Optional:-->
                     <sch:iccids>
                        <!--1 or more repetitions:-->
                        <sch:iccid>{{ICCID}}</sch:iccid>
                     </sch:iccids>
                     <!--Optional:-->
                     <sch:targetRatePlan>{{TARGETRATEPLAN}}</sch:targetRatePlan>
                     <!--Optional:-->
                     <sch:targetCommunicationPlan>{{TARGETCOMMUNICATIONPLAN}}</sch:targetCommunicationPlan>
                     <!--Optional:-->
                     <sch:targetSIMStatus>{{TARGETSIMSTATUS}}</sch:targetSIMStatus>
                     <sch:TrackingNumber>{{TRACKINGNUMBER}}</sch:TrackingNumber>
                     <!--Optional:-->
                     <sch:shipDate>{{SHIPDATE}}</sch:shipDate>
                     <!--Optional:-->
                     <sch:TrackingURL>{{TRACKINGURL}}</sch:TrackingURL>
                     <!--Optional:-->
                     <sch:shipmentStatus>{{SHIPMENTSTATUS}}</sch:shipmentStatus>
                  </sch:shipment>
               </sch:shipments>
            </sch:orderLineItem>
         </sch:orderLineItems>
         <!--You may enter ANY elements at this point-->
      </sch:AdvanceShipmentNotificationRequest>
   </soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>
